        <h1>2025 Federal Income Tax Brackets: Every Rate and Threshold</h1>
        <p class="qa-meta">Updated April 2026 &nbsp;|&nbsp; Based on IRS Rev. Proc. 2024-40 &nbsp;|&nbsp; Tax year 2025 (filed in 2026)</p>
        <p>The seven federal income tax rates for 2025 are 10%, 12%, 22%, 24%, 32%, 35%, and 37%. The income thresholds that trigger each rate were adjusted upward for inflation compared to 2024, so slightly more of your income falls into lower brackets.</p>
        <div class="year-nav">
          <a href="/tax-brackets-2025" class="active">2025 Brackets (Official)</a>
          <a href="/tax-brackets-2026">2026 Brackets (Projected)</a>
